Read AGENTS.md first — it is the canonical contract.
Treat rules/00-non-negotiable-rules.md as mandatory.
Do not import vendors — Ionic, Capacitor, Axios, Day.js, Virtuoso, Zustand, Zod, TanStack Query —
outside their owner package in src/packages. Components are UI-only; hooks live in *.hook.ts files.
Cross-module imports use @/modules/<feature> public surfaces only.
Per-file coverage is 95% (100% for pure logic); lint runs at zero warnings.
Do not edit generated .ai files; rebuild them with `npm run knowledge:build`.
